      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,6 @@\n+created: 2026-03-02\n+title: Styled widget color override fix\n+intro: >-\n+  Fixes color overrides for styled footer widgets. Widget configuration for `iconColor`\n+  and `textColor` now correctly propagates into styled widgets' render functions,\n+  and git status icons use semantic colors automatically."
